    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>A True Subway Series</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Dennis Consumano letter on World Series would be a true subway Series if players would use subway at least once to get to game</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''From Agbayani to Zimmer: A Primer'' (front page, Oct. 20):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''From Agbayani to Zimmer: A Primer'' (front page, Oct. 20):</p>
        <p>New York City has two great baseball teams and thousands of fans supporting them. But only the fans take the subway. Perhaps the Yankees and the Mets can show the fans their appreciation by taking the subway along with them for one of the games.</p>
        <p>DENNIS CONSUMANO  New York, Oct. 20, 2000</p>
      </block>
